    "actor": "https://uofa.net/synth/actor/morrison-lab-credibility-team",
    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed their required levels for MRL 2. The six non-assessed factors are explicitly scoped out per ASME V&V 40-2018 Table 4 at MRL 2. The CFD model is deemed credible for identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device. This model has been applied in clinical research to support regulatory submissions; the assessment team confirms the evidence package is sufficient for the intended decision context.",
